<br>
Are we going to attack them? <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ancientsaga.com/index.php" target="top">Ancient Saga</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Maxximuus Ludicruus - 60 Wizard<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE MAIL START--><a href="mailto:Maxximuus@earthlink.net"> Maxximuus@earthlink.net</a><!--EZCODE MAIL END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=viresttaelwaggler>Virest TaelWaggler</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Riding the Planes</span><br>  Posts: 835<br> <font color=#628CBC>(4/14/03 3:40:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=558.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://images.ucomics.com/images/ch/subsections/hobbes.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Syria</span><hr size=1> No.  Many administration officials have said there is no grounds or reason for them to attack Syria.<br>
<br>
