<br>
Technically we were allowed in Iraq due to the ceasefire but there's no such case here. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=valkyrisvalhalla>Valkyris Valhalla</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator<BR>Fim's Shoe Wench</span><br>  Posts: 406<br> <font color=#628CBC>(4/15/03 12:41:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=558.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://mywebpages.comcast.net/straubalexander/emoticon/bat_angel.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Syria</span><hr size=1> <br>
